  "texts": [
    "\"AI Governance and Policy\" reflects institutions' structured approaches to ensure responsible GenAI implementation.",
    "Institutions often establish multidisciplinary committees to integrate GenAI policies with existing frameworks, aligning AI deployment with organizational goals and regulatory requirements and focusing on legal and ethical compliance.",
    "\"Strategic Leadership and Decision Making\" highlights the crucial role of leadership in GenAI initiatives.",
    "High-level leaders drive GenAI integration through strategic planning and resource allocation, with integrated teams from IT, research, and clinical care fostering a culture of innovation and collaboration.",
    "Excerpts on these governance practices are detailed in Supplementary Table 3."
  ]
}